org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.condition

注释类型 ConditionalOnNotWebApplication


  • @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
 @Conditional(value=org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.condition.OnWebApplicationCondition.class)
public @interface ConditionalOnNotWebApplication
    Conditional that only matches when the application context is a not a web application context.
